%%  Tier 2 — Phases 6 · 7  |  Import Callback → EAM Status Writeback
%%  Flows: F6·IMPOR_CALLB  F7·STATUS_EVENT  F8·STATU_UPDAT
%%  Rendering: Mermaid v10.9+  |  sequenceDiagram
%%  Drill-downs: drill/06a-callback-import-results.mmd
%%               drill/08a-writeback-success-path.mmd  |  drill/08b-writeback-error-path.mmd
%%  See also: 00-overview-topology.mmd

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box External Systems
        participant ERP as Oracle ERP Cloud
        participant BIP as Oracle BIP SOAP
        participant EAM as EAM System
    end
    box OIC Integration Flows
        participant F6 as F6·IMPOR_CALLB
        participant F7 as F7·STATUS_EVENT
        participant F8 as F8·STATU_UPDAT
    end
    box OIC Platform
        participant AppEvt as OIC App Event Bus
    end
    box Oracle ATP DB
        participant ATP as ATP DB
    end

    %% ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    rect rgb(240,240,255)
    Note right of ERP: PHASE 6 · Import Result Processing  (F6·IMPOR_CALLB)<br/>Conn: IFP_PO_ORACL_ERP_CLOUD_CONNE (trigger) · IFP_PO_ORACL_BIP_SOAP_CONNE<br/>      IFP_PO_ATP_DB_CONNEC · APPLICATION_EVENT_CONNECTION<br/>Tracking: DOCUMENTID · SUMMARYSTATUS · tracking_var_3<br/>Drill-down: drill/06a-callback-import-results.mmd

    Note right of ERP: TRIGGER — ERP Cloud business event<br/>ESS "Import Purchase Orders" job completion callback<br/>NOT an OIC AppEvent — external push from ERP

    ERP->>F6: poimportorderscallback(DOCUMENTID, SUMMARYSTATUS, tracking_var_3)

    Note right of F6: STITCH (processor_3679 · processor_3328 · processor_3389)<br/>Init assigns — BATCH_ID · requestId · segment counters<br/>Global vars: gv_importSetID · segment index vars

    Note right of F6: ROUTER — 3 routes based on SUMMARYSTATUS / import type<br/>Routes 1 & 2 are mutually exclusive · see drill/06a for detail

    alt Route 1 — New import results [sc0]
        F6->>ATP: updateimportrequestid(BATCH_ID, requestId)
        F6->>BIP: callBIPReport() — PO import summary [SOAP]
        loop Segment rows — import summary
            F6->>ATP: insertImportDetailsintoATPDB(PODATA_RPT_OBJ_TAB, BATCH_ID)
        end
        F6->>ATP: callImportDetailsProcedure(BATCH_ID)
        F6->>BIP: callErrorReport() — PO import errors [SOAP]
        loop Segment rows — error report
            F6->>ATP: insertpoerroratp(INTERFACE_HEADER_KEY, ERROR_MESSAGE, BATCH_ID)<br/>⚠ ERROR_MESSAGE VARCHAR2(1000) — truncates long ERP error text
        end
        F6->>ATP: POErrorcallProcedure(BATCH_ID)
    else Route 2 — Extended import detail reports [sc1]
        F6->>ATP: updateimportrequestid2(BATCH_ID, requestId)
        F6->>BIP: callImportDetailsReport() [SOAP]
        F6->>ATP: poinserterroratp(rows)
        F6->>ATP: POerrordetailsrpt(rows)
        F6->>BIP: callImportDetailsErrorReport() [SOAP]
        loop Segment rows — detail error report
            F6->>ATP: insertImportDetailsError(rows)
        end
        F6->>ATP: callImportDetailsErrorProcedure(BATCH_ID)
    else Route 3 — ESS status-only / no report [sc6]
        F6->>ERP: DonloadZIPFile [ERP Cloud adapter — download result ZIP]
        F6->>F6: Email notification (no importable data)
    end

    F6->>ATP: FetchPOproecssdata(BATCH_ID)
    ATP-->>F6: Processed transaction summary
    F6->>F6: Notification — processed transaction report email (stageFile)

    F6->>AppEvt: PUBLISH PUBLISH_EAMPOSTATUSUPDAT [fire-and-forget]<br/>status=COMPLETE or ERROR — actual ESS import results

    critical Global scope fault
        option CATCH_ALL raised
            F6->>F6: Email notification → ehStop
    end
    end
    %% ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

    rect rgb(230,255,245)
    Note right of AppEvt: PHASE 7 · EAM Status Writeback  (F7·STATUS_EVENT → F8·STATU_UPDAT)<br/>⚠ This phase fires TWICE per batch:<br/>  Invocation 1 — from F5 PUBLISH (status=SUBMITTED, ESS still running)<br/>  Invocation 2 — from F6 PUBLISH (status=COMPLETE/ERROR, ESS done)<br/>Drill-downs: drill/08a-writeback-success-path.mmd · drill/08b-writeback-error-path.mmd

    AppEvt->>F7: SUBSCRIBE PUBLISH_EAMPOSTATUSUPDAT<br/>Conn: APPLICATION_EVENT_CONNECTION

    Note right of F7: Transformer maps PBatchID · p_Success_loadtype · p_Status_code → collocated payload

    F7->>F8: COLLOCATED CallPOEAMUpdateStatusIntegration(PBatchID, p_Success_loadtype, p_Status_code)<br/>[PRESEEDED_COLLOCATED_CONN_1741 — synchronous]

    Note right of F8: Triggered by F7 collocated invoke<br/>REST receive: poinboundmain via IFP_PO_OIC_REST_CONNEC<br/>Tracking: pbatchId · tracking_var_2 · tracking_var_3<br/>Init assigns — BATCH_ID · success/error flags · error code

    Note right of F8: UpdateEAMSuccessStatus scope<br/>See drill/08a-writeback-success-path.mmd for full loop detail

    F8->>ATP: GetSuccessPOs(BATCH_ID)
    ATP-->>F8: Successfully imported PO list

    opt Success POs exist [ROUTER: sc7]
        loop FOR each success PO
            F8->>EAM: PUT UpdateEAMPOSuccessStatus(PO number, APPROVED)<br/>[IFP_PO_EAM_REST_CONNEC — BASIC_AUTH]
            F8->>ATP: SentEAMUpdate(BATCH_ID, PO record)
            opt Cancel lines within this PO [ROUTER: sc0]
                loop FOR each cancel line
                    F8->>EAM: PUT UpdateCancelLineStatus(line, CANCELLED)
                end
            end
            F8->>ATP: Sent_EAMUpdate(BATCH_ID, record)
            critical Success writeback fault
                option CATCH_ALL raised
                    F8->>F8: ACTIVITY_STREAM_LOGGER (lg0)
            end
        end
    end

    Note right of F8: UpdateErrorinEAMHexagon scope<br/>See drill/08b-writeback-error-path.mmd for full nested loop detail

    F8->>ATP: getPOerrorrecords(BATCH_ID)
    ATP-->>F8: Error records per header

    opt Error headers exist [ROUTER: sc6]
        loop FOR each error header
            F8->>EAM: PUT EAMcallHdrErrorAPI(INTERFACE_HEADER_KEY, ERROR_CODE, ERROR_MSG)<br/>[IFP_PO_EAM_REST_CONNEC]
            F8->>EAM: PUT UpdateEAMPOStatus(PO header, ERROR)
            F8->>ATP: UpdateSentEAM(header error sent flag)
            critical Header error writeback fault
                option CATCH_ALL raised
                    F8->>F8: ACTIVITY_STREAM_LOGGER (lg4)
            end
            F8->>ATP: getpolineerrordetails(BATCH_ID, headerKey)
            loop FOR each error line
                F8->>EAM: PUT EAMCallLineErrorAPI(line key, line error details)
                F8->>ATP: SentEAMUpdate(line error sent)
                critical Line error writeback fault
                    option CATCH_ALL raised
                        F8->>F8: ACTIVITY_STREAM_LOGGER (lg3)
                end
            end
        end
    end

    critical Global scope fault
        option CATCH_ALL raised
            F8->>F8: Email notification → ehStop
    end
    end
